{"tid":625211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出前一丁概念店　閉門失火燒廚房","createTime":"2018-04-11T09:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T09:01:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a15c36171d3ac14df706b6056204b55b5680ca6","tid":625211,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:01:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20358390?_ga=2.108253058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20358390%3F_ga%3D2.108253058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=9Q56bAYsZhWDnGmmLrhNDsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d326aa1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F20358390%3F_ga%3D2.108253058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=cf707397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180411/20358390?_ga=2.108253058.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n出前一丁概念店　閉門失火燒廚房<br />\n<br />\n8.3K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 灣仔謝斐道535號一間麵店發生火警。昨早上6時許，位於商場3樓的日清食品出前一丁概念店發生火警，店內一個煮食爐疑因過熱冒煙起火，觸動自動灑水系統火警鐘。消防員趕至現場射水將火救熄，廚房輕微焚毀，由於起火時店舖已打烊關門，故無需疏散，亦無人受傷，火警並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n起火日式麵店由日清食品和辦館LOF10 Bar Dining合作，開設在銅鑼灣的「出前一丁x辦館 LOF 10」概念店，將日本出前一丁和港式地道風味大結合，讓港人試試新口味。"}]}